																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">1</div> <div class="vers-content">Now  Simon heard that Tryphon was gathering together a very great army, to invade the land of Juda, and to destroy it.</div></div></td>
																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">1</div> <div class="vers-content">And what did Simon, when he heard that Tryphon had levied a strong force, for Judaâ€™s invasion and overthrow?</div></div></td>
